TextEng: I've got a pass for the Gauntlet.
Me gots Gauntlet pass.
Anything interesting in this tavern?
Text: 이 주점에 볼 만한 게 있나?

TextEng: Anything neat in this place?
Let's see what you have for sale.
What's you got for sale?
Goodbye.
Give me the earnings for the week.
You give money made this week, maybe?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Come on, what harm is there in telling me?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 자, 좀 알려 준다고 해서 나쁠 것 없잖아?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Why you not tell? Nobody care if me know.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 왜 말 안 해? 내가 알아도 아무도 신경 안 써.

TextEng: I don't want to resort to force, but I will if you don't tell me.
Text: 힘으로 해결하고 싶진 않은데, 말 안 해 주면 그렇게 할 거야.

TextEng: Me not want to fight, but me will if you not tell.
Text: 나 싸움 하기 싫어. 근데 말 안 하면 할 거야.

TextEng: The Trade of Blades? What's that?
Trade of Blades? What that?
What is the Gauntlet, specifically?
What the Gauntlet be?
Why is this a big secret?
Text: 왜 이렇게 큰 비밀로 하는 거지?

TextEng: Why this all so secret-like?
What do I have to do now that I own the bar?
Text: 이제 내가 이 술집의 주인이 됐으니, 뭘 하면 되지?

TextEng: What me gots to do with this place now that me own it?
Text: 나 이제 여기 주인. 뭐 해야 돼?
